PersonCitySearchParameter

Parameter address-city:string

Searches based on the person's recorded city/village of address eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Person?address-city={city}

ResourcePerson
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesPerson
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
